public class CustomStageStyle
extends javafx.scene.control.ToolBar
    WindowDecoration, for undecorated stage this make your GUI also resizeable frist set your stage in start() on transparent .initStyle(StageStyle.TRANSPARENT); you can put this ToolBar for example: in the top of BorderPane
